    knitr,
    testthat,
    magrittr,
    BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: Visualization, CopyNumberVariation, Sequencing, Coverage, DNASeq, ChIPSeq, MethylSeq, DataImport
NeedsCompilation: no
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
